page.title: 13SOUTH STREET (WELLINGTON)
page.content: This street leads southwards out of town towards the By-pass,the Motorway & the blackdown hills.The main items in this area are Wellington Public School,The Cottage Hospital,The Health Centre,and the Baptist Church & Church Hall Also on this road we have Wellington Printers,A News Agent,A Travel Agent , An Estate Agent,3 Clothes Shops,2 Shoe Shops,A Fishmongers,A China & Glass Shop,A Florist,2 Building Societies,A Dairy/Wine Shop,A Sports Shop,A Cycle Shop,A Flooring Specialist,An Upholstery Shop,A Bookshop & A Wool Shop Further up the road is a Public House The road runs past several Private Housing Estates.
